info.name: Tumblr + Missing E: Widescreen Dashboard Fix
info.description: Missing E, a popular tumblr extension, has a widescreen dashboard feature. But Missing E is slow to update and tumblr breaks this feature often. This is a style to restore widescreen.
info.additionalInfo:
Only works with Missing E installed. Missing E can be found at http://missing-e.com/

v1 (2013/08/23): Initial upload.
